name: Pset_AirSideSystemInformation
definition: Attributes that apply to an air side HVAC system. HISTORY: New property set in IFC Release 1.0.

localizations.name: Systeminformation - luftseitig
localizations.definition: Attribute, die für ein luftseitiges HLK-System gelten HISTORY: Neue Eigenschaft, die in IFC Release 1.0 gesetzt wurde.

properties.name: Name
properties.definition: The name of the air side system.

properties.name: Description
properties.definition: The description of the air side system.

properties.name: AirSideSystemType
properties.definition: This enumeration specifies the basic types of possible air side systems (e.g., Constant Volume, Variable Volume, etc.).

localizations.name: Luftseite - Systemtyp
localizations.definition: Diese Aufzählung spezifiziert die Grundtypen möglicher luftseitiger Systeme (z.B. Constant Volume, Variable Volume, etc.).

properties.name: AirSideSystemDistributionType
properties.definition: This enumeration defines the basic types of air side systems (e.g., SingleDuct, DualDuct, Multizone, etc.).

localizations.name: 搬送方式
localizations.definition: 基本的な空調方式（単一ダクト、二重ダクト、マルチゾーン等）。

localizations.name: 반송방식
localizations.definition: 기본적인 공조 방식 (단일 덕트, 이중 덕트, 멀티존 등)

localizations.name: Luftseite - Systemverteilung
localizations.definition: Diese Aufzählung definiert die Grundtypen von luftseitigen Systemen (z.B. SingleDuct, DualDuct, DualDuct, Multizone, etc.).

properties.name: TotalAirflow
properties.definition: The total design supply air flowrate required for the system for either heating or cooling conditions, whichever is greater.

localizations.name: 給気量
localizations.definition: 暖房、冷房の条件の、いずれか大きい条件で要求される設計給気量。

localizations.name: 급기량
localizations.definition: 난방, 냉방 조건 중 하나 큰 조건에서 요구되는 설계 급기 량

localizations.name: Gesamt-Luftfluss
localizations.definition: Der für das System erforderliche Gesamtzuluftvolumenstrom für Heiz- oder Kühlbedingungen, je nachdem, welcher Wert größer ist.

properties.name: EnergyGainTotal
properties.definition: The total amount of energy gains for the spaces served by the system during the peak cooling conditions, plus any system-level total energy gains.

localizations.name: 総熱取得
localizations.definition: 居室の最大冷房負荷と空調システム（機器等）の再熱負荷による最大熱負荷。

localizations.name: 총 열 검색
localizations.definition: 거실 최대 냉방 부하 및 공조 시스템 (장비 등) 재열 부하에 의한 최대 열부하.

localizations.name: Gesamt-Energiegewinn
localizations.definition: Die Summe der Energiegewinne für die Räume, die das System während der Spitzenkühlbedingungen versorgt, zuzüglich der gesamten Energiegewinne auf Systemebene.

properties.name: AirflowSensible
properties.definition: The air flowrate required to satisfy the sensible peak loads.

localizations.name: 顕熱空調給気量
localizations.definition: 最大潜熱負荷に対応する給気量。

localizations.name: 현열 공조 급기 량
localizations.definition: 최대 잠열 부하에 대한 급기 량

localizations.name: Luftfluss - sensibel
localizations.definition: Der Luftdurchsatz, der erforderlich ist, um den empfindlichen Spitzenbelastungen gerecht zu werden.

properties.name: EnergyGainSensible
properties.definition: The sum of total energy gains for the spaces served by the system during the peak cooling conditions, plus any system-level sensible energy gains.

localizations.name: 顕熱空調負荷
localizations.definition: ピーク時各居室の最大冷房負荷と空調システムの顕熱負荷による最大顕熱負荷。

localizations.name: 현열 공조 부하
localizations.definition: 최대 각 거실 최대 냉방 부하 및 공조 시스템의 현열 부하에 의한 최대 현열 부하

localizations.name: Energiegewinn - sensibel
localizations.definition: Die Summe der Gesamtenergiegewinne für die Räume, die das System während der Spitzenkühlbedingungen versorgt, zuzüglich aller sinnvollen Energiegewinne auf Systemebene.

properties.name: EnergyLoss
properties.definition: The sum of energy losses for the spaces served by the system during the peak heating conditions.

localizations.name: 熱（エネルギー）ロス
localizations.definition: ピーク時空調システム最大暖房負荷を提供する際の熱ロス。

localizations.name: 열(에너지)로스
localizations.definition: 최대 공조 시스템 최대 난방 부하를 제공할 수있는 열 손실

localizations.name: Energieverlust
localizations.definition: Die Summe der Energieverluste für die vom System bedienten Räume während der Spitzenheizbedingungen.

localizations.name: 負荷の安全率
localizations.definition: 空調負荷計算用の安全率（割増係数）。

properties.name: HeatingTemperatureDelta
properties.definition: Heating temperature difference for calculating space air flow rates.

localizations.name: 暖房時送風温度差
localizations.definition: 空調送風量計算用の暖房給気温度差。

localizations.name: 난방시 돌풍 온도차
localizations.definition: 에어컨 송풍 량 계산을위한 난방 급기 온도차

properties.name: CoolingTemperatureDelta
properties.definition: Cooling temperature difference for calculating space air flow rates.

localizations.name: 冷房時送風温度差
localizations.definition: 空調送風量計算用の冷房給気温度差。

localizations.name: 냉방시 돌풍 온도차
localizations.definition: 에어컨 송풍 량 계산을위한 냉방 급기 온도차

properties.name: FanPower
properties.definition: Fan motor loads contributing to the cooling load.

localizations.name: 送風機電力消費量
localizations.definition: 送風機モーターからの熱取得。
